# Bicheng.me Personal Website

This is a personal website built with Vue 3, Vite, and modern web technologies. The site features a blog, projects showcase, photo gallery, and interactive demos.

## Architecture Overview

- **Framework**: Vue 3 with Composition API
- **Build Tool**: Vite with SSG (Static Site Generation)
- **UI Framework**: UnoCSS for atomic CSS
- **Routing**: File-based routing with [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts)
- **Content**: Markdown files in [pages/](mdc:pages/) directory
- **Components**: Vue components in [src/components/](mdc:src/components/)
- **Package Manager**: pnpm with workspace configuration in [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml)

## Key Features

- Static site generation with vite-ssg
- Markdown-based content with frontmatter
- Photo management and optimization
- RSS feed generation
- Dark/light theme support
- Interactive demos and visualizations
- SEO optimization with OG image generation

## Development Workflow

- Use `pnpm dev` to start development server
- Use `pnpm build` to build for production
- Scripts are managed in [scripts/](mdc:scripts/) directory
- Auto-imports configured for Vue composables and utilities

## Entry Points

- Main application: [src/main.ts](mdc:src/main.ts)
- Root component: [src/App.vue](mdc:src/App.vue)
- Build configuration: [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts)
- Styling configuration: [unocss.config.ts](mdc:unocss.config.ts)
